data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home with fresh paint, an open concept, and newer fixtures. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, indoor laundry, an oversized garage, and a master suite with a walk-in closet. This gorgeous home has everything you want for a growing family, investment, or a first-time home buyer. Schedule you're showing today!
